graph TB
    subgraph "Workbench Notebooks Component"
        BaseImages[Base Images<br/>CPU, CUDA, ROCm]
        WorkbenchImages[Workbench Images<br/>Jupyter, CodeServer, RStudio]
        RuntimeImages[Runtime Images<br/>Pipeline Execution]

        BaseImages -->|foundation for| WorkbenchImages
        BaseImages -->|foundation for| RuntimeImages
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates via| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    Dashboard -->|requests| NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller]
    NotebookController -->|creates| StatefulSet[Notebook StatefulSet]
    StatefulSet -->|deploys| WorkbenchPod[Workbench Pod<br/>Jupyter/CodeServer/RStudio]

    WorkbenchPod -->|uses| WorkbenchImages

    subgraph "External Services"
        PyPI[PyPI Index<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Git[Git Repositories<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Services"
        DSP[Data Science Pipelines]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
    end

    WorkbenchPod -->|installs packages| PyPI
    WorkbenchPod -->|accesses data| S3
    WorkbenchPod -->|clones repos| Git
    WorkbenchPod -->|registers models| ModelRegistry

    DSP -->|executes with| RuntimeImages
    RuntimePod[Runtime Pod] -->|uses| RuntimeImages
    RuntimePod -->|accesses artifacts| S3
    RuntimePod -->|registers models| ModelRegistry
    DSP -->|orchestrates| RuntimePod

    subgraph "Ingress"
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]
    end

    User -->|accesses| Route
    Route -->|authenticates| OAuthProxy
    OAuthProxy -->|forwards to| WorkbenchPod

    style BaseImages fill:#e8e8e8
    style WorkbenchImages fill:#4a90e2
    style RuntimeImages fill:#4a90e2
    style NotebookController fill:#7ed321
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321
    style DSP fill:#7ed321
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321
    style PyPI fill:#f5a623
    style S3 fill:#f5a623
    style Git fill:#f5a623
    style Route fill:#ffe6cc
    style OAuthProxy fill:#ffe6cc
